  "text": "Immunoblotting Analysis. Total protein was extracted from the tissues as described previously [CITATION_1] . The protein concentration of the sample was determined by the Bradford method. Samples were applied to 10% polyacrylamide SDS gels and subjected to electrophoresis, after which the proteins were immunoblotted with appropriate antibodies.",
